**Panel:** Compiler Architect · Language Theoretician · Distributed Systems & Concurrency · Storage Engineer · Domain Practitioners
**Evidence base:** src, runtime, std, benchmarks, tests, jade.md, profiling artefacts at results.json, results_full.json.
